events.name: Black Market
events.asm:
; NAME: Black Market
; GAMES: MP3_USA
; EXECUTION: Direct

ADDIU SP SP -48 ; Including 4 byte pad
SW RA 40(SP)
SW S2 36(SP)
SW S1 32(SP)
SW S0 28(SP)

JAL GetCurrentPlayerIndex
NOP

; Figure out which player item slots to fill
ADDU S0 R0 R0

LUI S1 hi(p1_item1)
ADDIU S1 S1 lo(p1_item1)

BEQ S0 V0 determineslot
NOP
ADDIU S0 S0 1

LUI S1 hi(p2_item1)
ADDIU S1 S1 lo(p2_item1)

BEQ S0 V0 determineslot
NOP
ADDIU S0 S0 1

LUI S1 hi(p3_item1)
ADDIU S1 S1 lo(p3_item1)

BEQ S0 V0 determineslot
NOP
ADDIU S0 S0 1

LUI S1 hi(p4_item1)
ADDIU S1 S1 lo(p4_item1)

; Figure out if the current player can even fit the item
determineslot:
ADDIU S2 R0 0xFF
LBU S0 0(S1)
BEQ S0 S2 giveitem ; First slot empty (0xFF)
NOP
ADDIU S1 S1 1
LBU S0 0(S1)
BEQ S0 S2 giveitem
NOP
ADDIU S1 S1 1
LBU S0 0(S1)
BEQ S0 S2 giveitem
NOP

; If we reached here, the player has too many items.
SW R0 16(SP) ; A4
SW R0 20(SP) ; A5
SW R0 24(SP) ; A6
ADDI A0 R0 0xB ; Character image (-1 for none)
LUI A1 hi(cannotGiveItemMsg)
ADDIU A1 A1 lo(cannotGiveItemMsg)
ADDU A2 R0 R0
JAL 0x800EC8EC ; ShowMessage
ADDU A3 R0 R0

JAL 0x800EC9DC
NOP
JAL 0x800EC6C8
NOP
JAL 0x800EC6EC
NOP
J exit
NOP

giveitem:
;BEGIN SHOW WELCOME MESSAGE CODE
SW R0 16(SP) ; A4
SW R0 20(SP) ; A5
SW R0 24(SP) ; A6
ADDI A0 R0 0xB ; Character image (-1 for none)
LUI A1 hi(gotItemMsg)
ADDIU A1 A1 lo(gotItemMsg)
ADDU A2 R0 R0
JAL 0x800EC8EC ; ShowMessage
ADDU A3 R0 R0

JAL 0x800EC9DC
NOP
JAL 0x800EC6C8
NOP
JAL 0x800EC6EC
NOP

;END SHOW WELCOME MESSAGE CODE

;BEGIN CHECK FOR COINS CODE

JAL GetCurrentPlayerIndex
NOP
ADDIU A0 V0 0
ADDIU A1 R0 10

JAL PlayerHasCoins ;Checks if player has 10 coins
NOP

BNE V0 R0 LoseCoins
NOP

;END CHECK FOR COINS CODE

;BEGIN MESSAGE DISPLAY CODE

SW R0 16(SP) ; A4
SW R0 20(SP) ; A5
SW R0 24(SP) ; A6
ADDI A0 R0 0xB ; Character image (-1 for none)
LUI A1 hi(poorMsg)
ADDIU A1 A1 lo(poorMsg)
ADDU A2 R0 R0
JAL 0x800EC8EC ; ShowMessage
ADDU A3 R0 R0

; The rest here perform the "wait for confirmation"
; and probably messagebox teardown.
JAL 0x800EC9DC
NOP
JAL 0x800EC6C8
NOP
JAL 0x800EC6EC
NOP
J exit
NOP

;BEGIN LOSE COIN CODE

LoseCoins:
JAL GetCurrentPlayerIndex ; Value is at V0
NOP
ADDIU A0 V0 0
ADDIU A1 R0 -10
JAL 0x800F5D44 ; Changes player's coin amount
NOP

JAL GetCurrentPlayerIndex ; Value is at V0
NOP
ADDIU A0 V0 0
ADDIU A1 R0 -10
JAL 0x800E1F48 ; Displays player's coin loss on-screen
NOP

ADDIU A0 R0 30
JAL SleepProcess ; Sleeps for 30 frames
NOP

;END LOSE COIN CODE

;BEGIN DETERMINE ITEM CODE

JAL 0x8000B16C
NOP

ADDIU A0 R0 0x2A
SLT S0 V0 A0
NOP

BNE S0 R0 getitemone
NOP

ADDIU A0 R0 0x54
SLT S0 V0 A0
NOP

BNE S0 R0 getitemtwo
NOP

ADDIU A0 R0 0x7E
SLT S0 V0 A0
NOP

BNE S0 R0 getitemthree
NOP

ADDIU A0 R0 0xA8
SLT S0 V0 A0
NOP

BNE S0 R0 getitemfour
NOP

ADDIU A0 R0 0xE6
SLT S0 V0 A0
NOP

BNE S0 R0 getitemfive
NOP

J getitemsix

;END DETERMINE ITEM CODE

;BEGIN GET ITEM CODE

getitemone:
ADDIU S2 R0 0x00 ; Mushroom value
SB S2 0(S1)
J bye
getitemtwo:
ADDIU S2 R0 0x01 ; Skeleton Key value
SB S2 0(S1)
J bye
getitemthree:
ADDIU S2 R0 0x06; Plunder Chest value
SB S2 0(S1)
J bye
getitemfour:
ADDIU S2 R0 0x08 ; Dueling Glove value
SB S2 0(S1)
J bye
getitemfive:
ADDIU S2 R0 0x0B ; Boo Bell value
SB S2 0(S1)

SB S2 0(S1)

ADDU A3 R0 R0

; The rest here perform the "wait for confirmation"

JAL 0x800EC9DC
NOP

NOP
JAL 0x800EC6EC
NOP

ADDIU SP SP -48 ; Including 4 byte pad
SW RA 40(SP)
SW S2 36(SP)
SW S1 32(SP)
SW S0 28(SP)

JAL GetCurrentPlayerIndex
NOP

; Figure out which player item slots to fill
ADDU S0 R0 R0

LUI S1 hi(p1_item1)
ADDIU S1 S1 lo(p1_item1)

BEQ S0 V0 determineslot
NOP
ADDIU S0 S0 1

LUI S1 hi(p2_item1)

BEQ S0 V0 determineslot
NOP
ADDIU S0 S0 1

LUI S1 hi(p3_item1)

BEQ S0 V0 determineslot
NOP
ADDIU S0 S0 1

LUI S1 hi(p4_item1)
ADDIU S1 S1 lo(p4_item1)

; Figure out if the current player can even fit the item
determineslot:
ADDIU S2 R0 0xFF
LBU S0 0(S1)
BEQ S0 S2 giveitem ; First slot empty (0xFF)
NOP
ADDIU S1 S1 1
LBU S0 0(S1)
BEQ S0 S2 giveitem
NOP
ADDIU S1 S1 1
LBU S0 0(S1)
